{# CONTENT SECTION #}
<section class="relative bg-white px-4 md:px-6 py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16">

      {# Left Column: Content #}
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        {# What is this report #}
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">What is this report?</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            <strong>The State of AI in Nepal 2026</strong> is the first comprehensive analysis of artificial intelligence adoption across Nepali industries. Based on research from 50+ organizations in Kathmandu and beyond, this report provides actionable insights for business leaders planning AI investments.
          </p>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Nepal ranks 150th globally in AI readiness, yet adoption is accelerating. Only 31.8% of businesses have dedicated AI budgets, and 56% cite lack of skilled manpower as their primary barrier. This report bridges the knowledge gap with practical frameworks tailored for Nepal's market conditions.
          </p>
        </div>

        {# Key Findings #}
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">Key findings</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-zunkiree-600">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-1">Only 20.77% of Nepal industries are AI-ready</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600">The technology sector leads at 45%, while manufacturing lags at 8%.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-zunkiree-600">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-1">39 AI companies operate in Nepal</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Up from 12 in 2023, with 4 new startups founded in 2025 alone.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-zunkiree-600">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-1">NPR 50K to 50M investment range</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Budget varies widely based on use case, from chatbots to full automation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {# What You Get #}
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">What you get:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {% for item in resource.whatYouGet %}
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 mt-1">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">{{ item }}</span>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>

        {# FAQ Section #}
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-6">Frequently asked questions</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">What industries does the report cover?</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-600">The report analyzes AI adoption across IT/Software, Financial Services, Healthcare, Manufacturing, Education, and Retail sectors in Nepal. Each industry section includes adoption rates, common use cases, and budget benchmarks.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">Is this report relevant for small businesses?</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Yes. We include specific guidance for SMEs with budget tiers starting at NPR 50,000. The report covers both enterprise AI implementations and accessible solutions for smaller organizations.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">How was the research conducted?</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-600">We surveyed 50+ organizations across Nepal, conducted interviews with 15 technology leaders, and analyzed publicly available data from government sources, industry associations, and international AI readiness indexes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# Right Column: Form #}
      <div class="lg:col-span-5" data-reveal>
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
